name.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Google Shopping List Copy To Clipboard

short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Copies text from shoppinglist.google.com to the clipboard, so you can import it into Keep or move it elsewhere

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
A very simple utility that allows you to copy the text from shoppinglist.google.com.

I created this because I like to keep my shopping lists in Google Keep, but Google Assistant isn't configured to do that anymore
